### GET all categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/results-categories
Accept: application/json

###

### CREATE category
POST http://localhost:8080/api/results-categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Prasmes"
}

###

### GET by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/results-categories/1
Accept: application/json

###

### UPDATE category
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/results-categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Prasmes"
}

###

### DELETE category
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/results-categories/4
